description:
God is someone who loves the spectacular and at the end of the world when it seems that all hope is lost, He will come in and rescue His followers in a manner that no drama, script writer or movie would be able to reenact. The Bible says that His eye is on the sparrow and He watches over His own. We need not be fearful for God will deliver His people!
